item.title: IT Apprentice
item.author: gmail@sivert.pw (Sivert V. Sæther)
item.description: This section of my blog serves as an index of technologies I’ve learned or became better at as an apprentice working in IT. 😀 It also serves the purpose of the required documentation Apprentices in Norway are supposed to do. 😳 Here are lists of stuff I’ll be writing about here; Programs Wordpress 💩 FreeRADIUS 🔮 Postgres 💾 Ansible 🔫 Operating Systems/Networking devices Debian 🎎 Mikrotik 📦 Cisco Meraki ☁️
